Once we started gathering, anyone else would have had to wait for us anyway -- we were at the top of the bracket, we had priority.  I don't know what time zone some of the other guilds who were in the bracket at the time are in -- Armonia is French, Fama is Japanese, don't know about VFA and Darksphere.  <br>
